We as a people pay taxes towards the running of the state for such services like NHS, Councils, Schools, welfare.
we as a people want the stop of all benefits to anyone who wasn’t born or haven’t lived here in the United kingdom for more than five years, also to place strict vetting on all immigrants from the EU and other countries and limit the amount of immigrants of amounts to less than 40,000 a year.
Immigration is good for this country we just want the right kind of immigration.
